       A time-travel experiment in which a robot probe is sent from        ª╞
       the year 2073 to the year 1973 goes terribly wrong thrusting        ª╞
       one of the project scientists, a man named Nicholas Sinclair        ª╞
       into a plague ravaged alternate time-line whose war weary           ª╞
       inhabitants are locked in a constant battle with killer robots      ª╞
       which are automatically being sent there from Sinclair's lab.       ª╞
       To escape this situation, Sinclair must find a similar time         ª╞
       machine in this alternate world and prevent the disaster from       ª╞
       ever happening.                                                     ª╞
